OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWatchdog head steps back   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom BBC chair probe       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The head of the watchdog probing the   
OL,6, appointment of the BBC chairman has    
OL,7, stepped back because of past contact   
OL,8, between the pair.                      
OL,10,FWilliam Shawcross, the commissioner for
OL,11,Fpublic appointments, was set to examine
OL,12,Fhow Richard Sharp got the job.         
OL,14,FIt followed controversy over Mr Sharp's
OL,15,Frole in loan talks involving then prime
OL,16,Fminister Boris Johnson, who nominated  
OL,17,Fhim for the role.                      
OL,19,FThe government has insisted Mr Sharp   
OL,20,Fwas appointed on merit.                
